WEB SERVICE

service(server) servlet clients

in netbeans:


file -> new proj -> java web -> web application
give name
glassFish server, java ee 7
finish

right click -> new web service
give name, package com.myservice

web service wali file pe right click
add operation 
change return

created proj pe right click
build
deploy

web service right click test web service

====================================================

file -> new proj -> java web -> web application
give name (client)

client ke index.html ke body me
windows -> ide tools -> palette
form action CalculatorServlet, method get
button ke liye <input type="subit" value="Submit">


proj pe right click -> new web service client
proj browse, package default

client proj pe right click
new -> servlet -> name CalculatorServlet
check checkbox

in CalculatorServlet.java file
drag drop saare operations

phir 
double num1, num2;
num1=Double.parseDouble(request.getParameter("number1"));
num2=Double.parseDouble(request.getParameter("number2"));
op mein call 4 operations
addition(num1,num2) and so on

client proj ko clean and build
form wale index.html, right click and run file`